---
title: Pulled Pork Chili Bowl with Cheesy Taquitos
description: Leave the crockpot in the cabinet! These pulled pork chilli bowls are quick, filling and full of flavour. Top them with fresh lime crema and use the cheesy taquitos as delicious dippers!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chili-au-porc-effiloche-e1fd7f8d.jpg
